# 💰 Software Cost Estimation Tool

A modern, interactive web application that helps developers and project managers estimate **effort**, **development time**, **productivity**, and **team size** using industry-standard models like **COCOMO**.

> 📊 Built for academic use, personal planning, and project estimations — just enter your code or KLOC and get realistic results.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔢 **KLOC Calculator** – Paste your code to automatically calculate lines of code
- 📐 **Model Selection** – Supports Basic, Intermediate, and Detailed (COCOMO variants)
- 🧠 **Cost Drivers** – Select influencing factors for better estimation (Intermediate Model)
- 📅 **Effort, Time, Staff Size, Productivity Calculations**
- 📊 **Instant Results** – Clean UI and real-time outputs
- ✅ **Mobile-friendly** – Responsive design with modern layout

---

## 🖥️ Tech Stack

- **HTML5** – Structure
- **CSS3** – Styling with modern UI and responsive layout
- **JavaScript (Vanilla)** – Core logic and interactivity

> No libraries or frameworks — 100% handcrafted

